    HomePage

    public class PokeSceneWithHeaderAndAggregateBlastoiseCharizard
extends PokeSceneWithHeader
    This class create a sort of double inheritance because it instantiates a PokeSceneWithBlastoiseCharizard. This class should be used to be extended by scenes that want the header containing the username and the number of pokeball hold (this one only for normal user), and the background with the two pokemon displayed.
